=====Usage notes=====
* In Cantonese, when {{lang|zh|з•Җ}} is used as a [[ditransitive]] verb meaning вҖңto giveвҖқ, the [[indirect object]] usually follows the [[direct object]].
* In a [[passive voice|passive-voice]] sentence in Cantonese, {{lang|zh|з•Җ}} is always followed by an object and not a verb, unlike Mandarin {{zh-l|иў«}} which can be followed by an object or a verb. {{zh-l|дәә|tr=jan4}} can be used as a dummy object when the [[doer]] is not specified.

